Interface AttributeConstraint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Refinement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttributeConstraintImpl

    public interface AttributeConstraint
extends Refinement
    A representation of the model object 'Attribute Constraint'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Cardinality
    • Reversed
    • Attribute
    • Comparison
